{"tid":2364840,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方埋伏拘捕1男 涉西貢警署外塗鴉燈柱 寫侮辱國安法字句","createTime":"2021-01-13T09:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:17:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"540b6487d068cad7b1e13bc630385ab5f23f19c8","tid":2364840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/da5fcd7835e054d53ed38417ebba0890/2021/01/a60946b5930ae3f37263619f74e43f45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Fda5fcd7835e054d53ed38417ebba0890%2F2021%2F01%2Fa60946b5930ae3f37263619f74e43f45.jpg&h=e2d8ac9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名年約50歲男子，涉嫌在警署外牆塗鴉。警方指，去年11月6日和本月8日，在西貢警署外牆發現被人以黑色油性筆寫上「721」字眼，經調查後昨日派員到西貢福民路一帶進行埋伏，發現一名男子，在西貢警署外一段福民路的兩條燈柱上，以黑色油性筆寫上侮辱港區國安法的字句，警員隨即上前，以涉嫌刑事毀壞把他拘捕。 這名男子報稱是售貨員，警方不排除他與其他案件有關，或會向刑事毁壞以外方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2374659&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7e75b2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374659</a>"},{"pid":"2233b8c8cec155a95c9a8f0647b6c5887d72e427","tid":2364840,"uid":304431,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"721呢？721去了哪裡"},{"pid":"b0513c5b71fc95d8e5de48e36e05d96530b3d57e","tid":2364840,"uid":185854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"捉呢d都埋伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef61ed119829ee93aa54f8f9095f51c947b1c3c","tid":2364840,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:47:40.000Z","msg":"咩大罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\